data.description: Discover Central Beach living in this perfectly situated home, amidst mature oak trees on an expansive nearly half-acre double lot. This residence features 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, with a spacious floor plan perfect for entertaining with an abundance of natural light. The generous private lot provides ample room for future enhancements including a pool. With sturdy CBS construction, a brand-new roof to be installed and the added security of accordion hurricane shutters, this is a must see. Short walk to Beaches, Ocean Drive, shopping, & restaurants.
